content.html: A very COVID christmas 😷🎄🌡😭 Not how I was expecting to spend the holidays AT ALL but I guess thankful for quarantine companions, American eggnog, reality TV and cuddly pups. Please please keep taking precautions, testing regularly and get boosters if you haven’t already ❤️‍🩹

A very COVID christmas 😷🎄🌡😭

Not how I was expecting to spend the holidays AT ALL but I guess thankful for quarantine companions, American eggnog, reality TV and cuddly pups.

Please please keep taking precautions, testing regularly and get boosters if you haven’t already ❤️‍🩹

photo.alt: Selfie where I look sick but throwing up a peace sign and Haleigh has a beer. A cute dog is curled up at her feet.
My view from the couch. You can see my legs under a fuzzy blanket, a dog on my lap, a decked out Christmas tree and a movie on the TV.
